Titolo: Rama (video game)

Anno: 1996

Descrizione: Rama is a first-person adventure game developed and published by Sierra On-Line in 1996. The game is based on Arthur C. Clarke's books Rendezvous with Rama (1973) and Rama II (1989) and supports both MS-DOS and Windows. In 1998, a PlayStation version was released in Japan.
It is the second Rama game to be produced. Rendezvous with Rama, a text adventure, was released in 1984 by Telarium.